text: Rhombophyllum is a genus of succulent plants in the ice plant family, Aizoaceae. Members of the genus are native to southern Africa. ==Species== *Rhombophyllum albanense (L.Bolus) H.E.K.Hartmann *Rhombophyllum dolabriforme Schwantes *Rhombophyllum dyeri (L.Bolus) H.E.K.Hartmann *Rhombophyllum nelii Schwantes *Rhombophyllum rhomboideum (Salm-Dyck) Schwantes ==References== Category:Aizoaceae genera
title: Rhombophyllum
